product.name: Artpuch Outdoor Roller Shade 8' W x 8' H, Gray Exterior Cordless Patio Shades Roll Up Blinds with Splicing Design, 2 Poles and 1 Piece Fabric
product.description:
Outdoor Roller Shades
Roller Shade with Valance
90% Sun Shade Cloth
40% Black Shade Cloth
70% Black Shade Cloth
Artpuch stems from the cherish for the outdoor time with family. We focus on outdoor shading products such as outdoor roller blinds and shade sails. They can be used in various scenarios, providing sun protection and privacy, allowing you and your family to enjoy the outdoors to the fullest. Choosing Artpuch means choosing every happy moment with your family in the sunshine.
product.bullet_points:
• Spliced of 2 Poles, 1 Piece Fabric: When you receive the package, you will notice that the roller blind's tube is split in two. This design is intended to increase the efficiency of transportation. Please assemble the tube and put the complete piece of fabric into it(Follow the installation steps in the instructions)
• 90% UV Blocking & Cooling Comfort: Artpuch exterior roller shade uses 220 GSM 100% pure non-recycled HDPE shade fabric. Blocking 90% of harmful UV rays, these outdoor shades protect privacy and reduce sun glare.They also cut down on heating and cooling costs, saving you money
• Easy to Install: Package come with all the necessary accessories and step-by-step instructions, and also have installation videos for quick and easy setup so you can enjoy your outdoor scene with ease. Set includes 8 drywall plastic anchors, 8 classic 304 stainless steel screws, 2 durable roller brackets, 2 durable bungee brackets and 2 beautiful bungee cords ensuring stress-free installation and scene enhancement. If anything is missing, please let us know and we will take care of it for you
• Multiple Applications: The roll up shades are the perfect fit for a wide range of outdoor spaces, including porches, gazebos, patios, backyards, decks, balconies, pergolas, and more. Tailor the ambiance of your chosen scene with ease and style, from tranquil mornings with a cup of coffee to vibrant garden parties or cozy family dinners
• Note: Artpuch outdoor roller shade shipping box is smaller than the actual product size. The fabric is neatly folded, and the poles feature a connector-based design, allowing for efficient packaging without compromising on quality.Rest assured, you'll receive the full-sized, high-quality shade as described—ready for installation
